 Technical Implementation Details

 Frontend Architecture

**Component Hierarchy**:
```
App
├── Dashboard
│   ├── Header (Navigation, Login)
│   ├── FilterPanel
│   │   ├── RegionFilter
│   │   ├── YearRangeSlider
│   │   ├── ScoreRangeFilter
│   │   └── ComponentMultiSelect
│   ├── VisualizationContainer
│   │   ├── Heatmap (D3.js)
│   │   ├── TrendChart (Recharts)
│   │   ├── ScatterPlot (D3.js)
│   │   └── ComparisonTable
│   ├── TableView (Sortable, Filterable)
│   └── ExportPanel
└── Authentication
    ├── Login
    ├── Register
    └── PasswordReset
```

**State Management** (Redux):
- `filters`: Current user selections (region, year, components, score range)
- `data`: Fetched datasets (countries, scores, components)
- `ui`: Dashboard state (selected view, loading status, error messages)
- `user`: Authentication info (username, permissions, preferences)

 Backend API Examples

**GET /api/scores/country/SGP?year=2025**
```json
{
  "iso3": "SGP",
  "country": "Singapore",
  "year": 2025,
  "scores": {
    "overall": 83.9,
    "rule_of_law": 88.2,
    "government_size": 81.5,
    "regulatory_efficiency": 85.6,
    "open_markets": 81.3
  },
  "components": {
    "property_rights": 89,
    "judicial_effectiveness": 87,
    "government_integrity": 88,
    "tax_burden": 82,
    "government_spending": 75,
    "fiscal_health": 86,
    "business_freedom": 88,
    "labor_freedom": 78,
    "monetary_freedom": 84,
    "trade_freedom": 83,
    "investment_freedom": 85,
    "financial_freedom": 88
  }
}
```

**GET /api/trends/country/VNM?start_year=2015&end_year=2025**
```json
{
  "country": "Vietnam",
  "trend": [
    {"year": 2015, "score": 64.7},
    {"year": 2016, "score": 65.2},
    ...
    {"year": 2025, "score": 73.2}
  ],
  "change_10yr": "+8.5",
  "avg_annual_change": "+0.85",
  "gdp_growth_correlation": 0.76,
  "policy_highlights": ["Trade liberalization 2017", "Business registration reform 2019"]
}
```

